HR NO. 254 ENROLLED
WHEREAS, in addition to his service at the Louisiana State Capitol, Ty interned
with United States House Speaker Mike Johnson in Washington, D.C., in 2024; and
WHEREAS, Ty Hebert is deserving of recognition for his initiative, reliability,
ability to balance administrative and substantive work, and service with the Acadiana
Legislative Delegation.
THEREFORE, BE IT RESOLVED that the House of Representatives of the
Legislature of Louisiana does hereby commend Acadiana Legislative Delegation student
worker Ty Hebert on the occasion of his graduation from Louisiana State University and
does hereby express enduring appreciation for his outstanding service to the delegation and
its members.
